	<h1 class="title">皮克斯分享设计心得：我们做了这 4 件事，让故事更迷人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101857/small/101857.jpg?1429073860" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">谢舒敏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-08 13:06:21 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15738/medium/15738.jpg?1444238228" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


